{"tid":1301904,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"7.13 光復上水 Update","createTime":"2019-07-09T18:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T07:11:12.000Z","uid":154627,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"db48eb6ca26d769beb0ae6abd691ba0c99c1bf71","tid":1301904,"uid":154627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:25:40.000Z","msg":"【713 光復上水UPDATE】<br />\n今晚我們同接近20位警方人員係上水警署開會商討遊行路線及安排，由於警方評估後認為今次遊行將會有大量參與者，而原集合地點 &ndash; 「上水花園第一號」無法容納參與遊行的人士，故此建議我們將遊行集合地點改為面積更大的 -「北區運動場籃球場」，以便容納更加多的參與人士。<br />\n<br />\n在跟警方商討後，我們決定接納警方的建議，將集合地點改為「北區運動場籃球場」，敬請各位留意。<br />\n<br />\n「不反對通知書」仍在批核階段，相信我們於短期內會收到警方就是次遊行發出的「不反對通知書」。如有進一步的消息，我們會盡快向各位公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消息發佈:<br />\n請留意本專頁 或<br />\nTelegram Channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Assemble713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAssemble713&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=7468ed59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Assemble713</a><br />\n<br />\n招募義工:<br />\n由於我們將會進行街站宣傳，另外，警方要求我們安排糾察或義工沿途維持秩序，如有意成為義工，請經INBOX聯絡我們  或<br />\n加入Telegram 群組:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LkY6chN10ReoCdIwHIq9ug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLkY6chN10ReoCdIwHIq9ug&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=89a1d27a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LkY6chN10ReoCdIwHIq9ug</a>"},{"pid":"cc6475bd1a63444c55c1cf15ba253fb75b4b0451","tid":1301904,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9310eb572dcf95643bdd4fdeb7759c4350ec7e5","tid":1301904,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets